ax-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;text-align:center;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Gj4Xa3wGN5icicpqKhciaBrm2ibkgMGtUvMywWPREK0hBtEKAvy4SFVreb67Jeqibn1bYjpIkynI4Dc0dZneKyfqjeA/0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7&quot; data-w=&quot;500&quot; _width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Gj4Xa3wGN5icicpqKhciaBrm2ibkgMGtUvMywWPREK0hBtEKAvy4SFVreb67Jeqibn1bYjpIkynI4Dc0dZneKyfqjeA/0&quot; style=&quot;max-width:100%;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;visibility:visible !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-wrap:normal;min-height:1em;white-space:pre-wrap;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&#039;Helvetica Neue&#039;, Helvetica, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;, &#039;Microsoft YaHei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;pre style=&quot;max-width:100%;color:#3E3E3E;font-size:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-variant:inherit;font-weight:inherit;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;line-height:21px;background-color:#B2CF73;white-space:pre-wrap;word-wrap:break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;&quot;&gt;         人生，就是一种糊涂，一份模糊，说懂不懂，说清不清，糊里糊涂，含含糊糊。看清，麻烦，看懂，伤感。世上之事，太过缠，世上之人，太过纠缠。看不清，一种轻松，一份安宁。\r\n何况，人生看不惯的东西真多，\r\n1、主动，是因为在乎。不联系，是因为觉得自己多余。\r\n2、走不进的世界就不要硬挤了，难为了别人，作贱了自己，何必呢？\r\n3、有时候，不小心知道了一些事，才发现自己所在乎的事是那么可笑。\r\n4、谁不虚伪，谁不善变，谁都不是谁的谁。又何必把一些人，一些事看的那么重要。&lt;/pre&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;max-width:100%;word-